{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-427-n-sequences","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 427: mfululizo wa n","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Niz celih brojeva $S = \\{s_i\\}$ naziva se nizom dužine $n$ ako ima $n$ elemenata i svaki element $s_i$ zadovoljava $1 \\le s_i \\le n$. Ukupan broj različitih nizova dužine $n$ je $n^n$.</p>\n<p>Kwa mfano, mfululizo $S = \\{1, 5, 5, 10, 7, 7, 7, 2, 3, 7\\}$ ni mfululizo wa 10.</p>\n<p>Za bilo koji niz $S$, neka $L(S)$ označava dužinu najdužeg uzastopnog podniza sa jednakim vrednostima. Na primer, za gore dati niz $S$, važi $L(S) = 3$, zbog tri uzastopne sedmice.</p>\n<p>Izračunajte $f(n) = \\sum L(S)$ za sve sekvence celih brojeva $n$ $S$.</p>\n<p>Kwa mfano, $f(3) = 45$, $f(7) = 1\\,403\\,689$ na $f(11) = 481\\,496\\,895\\,121$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $f(7\\,500\\,000)\\bmod 1\\,000\\,000\\,009$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5181000cf542c51002a","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302097,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-427-n-sequences"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function nSequences() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nnSequences();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>nSequences()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>97138867</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(nSequences(), 97138867);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-427-n-sequences","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-428-necklace-of-circles","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-426-box-ball-system","id":"5900f5181000cf542c51002a","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-427-n-sequences"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}